OL,3,CPrison staff 'poisoned' by inmates
OL,4,Cafter curry allegedly spiked, union
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FA union representing prison officers
OL,8,Fhas called for a "full investigation"
OL,9,Finto reports of a "mass poisoning" of
OL,10,Fstaff at a prison in Kent.
OL,12,FThe Criminal Justice Workers Union
OL,13,Fsaid that 25 people were affected in
OL,14,Fthe incident at HMP Swaleside on the
OL,15,FIsle of Sheppey.
OL,17,FSouth East Coast Ambulance Service
OL,18,Fconfirmed that three people working at
OL,19,Fthe men's high-security prison were
OL,20,Ftaken to hospital.
