OL,3,CPrison staff 'poisoned' by inmates
OL,4,Cafter curry allegedly spiked, union
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FAndy Hamlin, Criminal Justice Workers
OL,8,FUnion, said: "The Criminal Justice
OL,9,FWorkers Union are concerned at the
OL,10,Freports from HMP Swaleside regarding
OL,11,Fthe deliberate poisoning of staff by
OL,12,Fprisoners working in the staff canteen
OL,13,Fwith Spice.
OL,15,F"Although it is not unusual for
OL,16,Fprisoners to be working staff
OL,17,Fcanteens, they are expected to be the
OL,18,Flow risk, which clearly hasn't
OL,19,Fhappened in this case.
