OL,3,CPrison staff 'poisoned' by inmates
OL,4,Cafter curry allegedly spiked, union
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"Spice is a synthetic psychoactive
OL,8,Fsubstance, designed to replicate the
OL,9,Fhigh of illegal drugs.
OL,11,F"It can cause symptoms such as
OL,12,Fbreathing difficulties,
OL,13,Fhallucinations, raised heart rate and
OL,14,Fis extremely dangerous to those pre
OL,15,Fexisting illnesses."
OL,17,FIt is understood that none of the
OL,18,Fstaff were in critical condition and
OL,19,Fall have since been discharged from
OL,20,Fhospital.
