OL,3,CPrison staff 'poisoned' by inmates
OL,4,Cafter curry allegedly spiked, union
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FMr Hamlin added that staff were
OL,8,Finstructed not to discuss the incident
OL,9,Fon May 9, which he claimed was the
OL,10,Fmanagement's attempt to "play down the
OL,11,Fincident".
OL,13,FHe said: "Our members have raised
OL,14,Fvalid concerns, and believe the senior
OL,15,Fmanagement team at HMP Swaleside have
OL,16,Fattempted to play down the incident,
OL,17,Fwith staff being instructed not to
OL,18,Fdiscuss the incident or mention it on
OL,19,Fsocial media.
