OL,3,CPrison staff 'poisoned' by inmates
OL,4,Cafter curry allegedly spiked, union
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"This has led staff to believe the
OL,8,Fsenior management team are
OL,9,Fprioritising the establishment's
OL,10,Freputation, over the health and safety
OL,11,Fof its staff.
OL,13,F"The CJWU demand HMPPS (HM Prison and
OL,14,FProbation Service) carry out a full
OL,15,Finvestigation into this incident,
OL,16,Fwhich resulted in 25 staff being
OL,17,Fpoisoned, nine South East Coast
OL,18,FAmbulances attending and an emergency
OL,19,Fincident unit being set up within the
OL,20,Festablishment.
