OL,3,CPrison staff 'poisoned' by inmates
OL,4,Cafter curry allegedly spiked, union
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,F"HMPPS and local senior management
OL,8,Fteam at HMP Swaleside must do more to
OL,9,Fprotect the health and safety of its
OL,10,Fstaff."
OL,12,FA Prison Service spokesperson said: "A
OL,13,Fnumber of staff were taken ill
OL,14,Ffollowing an incident at HMP Swaleside
OL,15,Flast week but have all now returned to
OL,16,Fwork.
OL,18,F"There is an ongoing investigation and
OL,19,Fit would be inappropriate to comment
OL,20,Ffurther at this stage."
